<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="109" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,728,1907]" pageId="2" pageNumber="109">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,1809,1835]" pageId="2" pageNumber="109">Ecology.</emphasis>
<materialsCitation county="This" elevation="700" location="Kabili Sepilok Forest Reserve" municipality="Kawag Forest Reserve" pageId="2" pageNumber="109" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Sabah">
This species seems to restricted to highlands of 
<quantity box="[848,983,1808,1835]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="109" unit="m" value="700.0" valueMax="900.0" valueMin="500.0">
<elevation box="[848,983,1808,1835]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="109" unit="m" value="700.0" valueMax="900.0" valueMin="500.0">500–900 m</elevation>
</quantity>
.a.s.l. 
<collectingCounty box="[1042,1092,1808,1834]" pageId="2" pageNumber="109">This</collectingCounty>
species was not found in lowland forests of eastern 
<collectingRegion box="[410,478,1844,1870]" country="Malaysia" name="Sabah" pageId="2" pageNumber="109">Sabah</collectingRegion>
that the authors have sampled in (i.e., 
<collectingMunicipality box="[922,1181,1845,1871]" pageId="2" pageNumber="109">Kawag Forest Reserve</collectingMunicipality>
, 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:A4023F5CC974FFAC87B261768B27E320:2974D891C974FFAC838F644989EDE320" county="This" municipality="Kawag Forest Reserve" name="Kabili Sepilok Forest Reserve" pageId="2" pageNumber="109" stateProvince="Sabah">Kabili Sepilok Forest Reserve</location>
and 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:A4023F5CC974FFAC87B261768B27E320:2974D891C974FFAC860264258B33E320" box="[295,559,1880,1907]" county="This" municipality="Kawag Forest Reserve" name="Tabin Wildlife Reserve" pageId="2" pageNumber="109" stateProvince="Sabah">Tabin Wildlife Reserve</location>
)
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
